{"tid":2321339,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐韓美軍將向南韓政府交還12處駐軍基地","createTime":"2020-12-11T12:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T12:15:42.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ee5d1cd3bf0192538c3c6a347bced147a91134","tid":2321339,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"美國與南韓達成協議，駐韓美軍將向南韓政府，交還12處駐軍基地。<br />\n<br />\n有關地皮分別位於首爾市、京畿道、大邱市、廣尚北道及江原道，總面積超過146萬平方米。南韓政府將用作興建住宅大廈、公園及傳染病專門醫院。<br />\n<br />\n兩國早在2002年開始商討交還地皮安排，韓方將先行承擔所收回基地的污染淨化費用，日後雙方再協商分擔費用、環境管理及制定污染管理標準等事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564857-20201211.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564857-20201211.htm&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmridffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=de5fe9d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564857-20201211.htm&h=777e5327\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564857-20201211.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8cf70258e8edce0d7edcde130e04e54b59cc761a","tid":2321339,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}